## 1. Fugl-Meyer Assessment (Clinical Foundation)

**Title:**
Fugl-Meyer Assessment of Sensorimotor Recovery After Stroke

**Year:**
1975

**Why we use it**

```text
Ground truth clinical scale
Stroke severity measurement
Motor recovery scoring
```

**Used in**

```text
Entire project
Labels
Severity interpretation
Clinical validation
```

Reference explaining FMA: [Understanding the Fugl-Meyer Assessment](https://www.neurolutions.com/after-stroke/understanding-the-fugl-meyer-assessment/?utm_source=chatgpt.com) ([Neurolutions][1])

